                        "type": "offensive_action",
                        "text": "<b>Requirements</b> A creature is grabbed in the glabrezu\u2019s pincer. <b>Effect</b> The glabrezu pulls the grabbed creature up to 5 feet closer, then makes two claw Strikes against it. Those Strikes count as one attack when determining a treachery demon\u2019s multiple attack penalty, and the penalty doesn\u2019t increase until after both Strikes.",
